I found a concrete migration bug rather than just a cleanliness issue: the app now renders v3 messages from `AppSyncStore`, but opening a session still only triggers the old `fetchMessages` path. That means existing transcripts can stay empty until a fresh push arrives. I’m patching the visibility path to hydrate the visible session through `SyncNode`.
